is Gehringer]] \u2013 mastering\n* Josh Gudwin \u2013 mixing\n* Ali Khazaee \u2013 typography\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019\u20132020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardargentinahot100|12|artist=Dua Lipa|rowheader=true|accessdate=6 April 2020|refname=\"argentinachart\"}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Australia|2|artist=Dua Lipa|song=Don't Start Now|rowheader=true|accessdate=14 November 2019|refname=\"australianchart\"}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|6|artist=Dua Lipa|song=Don't Start Now|rowheader=true|accessdate=11 January 2020|refname=\"austrianchart\"}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|2|artist=Dua Lipa|song=Don't Start Now|rowheader=true|accessdate=7 December 2019|refname=\"flanderschart\"}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|3|artist=Dua Lipa|song=Don't Start Now|rowheader=true|accessdate=15 February 2020|refname=\"walloniachart\"}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Bolivia ([[Monitor Latino]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Print/Bolivia/general/20191209|title=Bolivia General|language=Spanish|accessdate=21 March 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321184638/http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Print/Bolivia/general/20191209|archivedate=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Brazil ([[Top 100 Brasil]])<ref name=\"brazilianchart\">{{cite web|url=https://charts.crowley.com.br/index.html|title=Top 100 Brasil \u2013 09/03/2020 - 13/03/2020|publisher=[[Crowley Broadcast Analysis]]|accessdate=21 March 2020|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n| 53\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Bulgaria ([[PROPHON]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.prophon.org/charts/24-jan-2020|title=\u0410\u0440\u0445\u0438\u0432 \u043a\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438|publisher=PROPHON|language=Bulgarian|accessdate=7 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 3\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|3|artist=Dua Lipa|rowheader=true|accessdate=19 Febr